            <title>[SPR-11798] NPE in HttpSessionEventPublisher</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-11798</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I am trying to run spring 4 mvc application in servlet 3 container (tomcat 7).&lt;br/&gt;
I have implemented ApplicationListener&amp;lt;ApplicationEvent&amp;gt; to receive notification on session creation and session destroy events. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Whenever I try to access my application, I am getting NPE at below code in HttpSessionEventPublisher&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;getContext(event.getSession().getServletContext()).publishEvent(e);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have further debugged the code and noticed that following getContext method is returning null instead of applicationContext. The webapplication context is not being set for key &quot;WebApplicationContext.ROOT_WEB_APPLICATION_CONTEXT_ATTRIBUTE&quot; in servlet context hence causing NPE.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks,&lt;br/&gt;
Amit&lt;/p&gt;</description>
